    public static enum CefRequest.TransitionFlags
extends java.lang.Enum<CefRequest.TransitionFlags>
    Transition qualifiers. Any of the core values above can be augmented by one or more qualifiers. These qualifiers further define the transition.(转换限定符。上面的任何核心值都可以通过一个或多个限定符进行扩充。这些限定符进一步定义了转换。)

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      TT_BLOCKED_FLAG
      Attempted to visit a URL but was blocked.(尝试访问URL，但被阻止。)
      TT_CHAIN_END_FLAG
      The last transition in a redirect chain.(重定向链中的最后一个转换。)
      TT_CHAIN_START_FLAG
      The beginning of a navigation chain.(导航链的开始。)
      TT_CLIENT_REDIRECT_FLAG
      Redirects caused by JavaScript or a meta refresh tag on the page.(由JavaScript或页面上的元刷新标记引起的重定向。)
      TT_FORWARD_BACK_FLAG
      Used the Forward or Back function to navigate among browsing history.(使用“前进”或“后退”功能在浏览历史记录之间导航。)
      TT_SERVER_REDIRECT_FLAG
      Redirects sent from the server by HTTP headers.(通过HTTP标头从服务器发送的重定向。)
